            <li><strong>Variety:</strong> With a wide range of scents and formulations, we have a soap for every preference and skin type.</li>
            <li><strong>Affordable Luxury:</strong> Enjoy high-quality, luxurious soaps at prices that won’t break the bank.</li>
        </ul>
